name: Second Skin Tattoo Canvas 4x6
description:
Second Skin Tattoo Canvases are skin-like canvases that act, feel, hold a stencil perfectly, no hair spray, no waiting over night...and tattoo just like real skin! Tattooing is an art, tattoos are art, why not start displaying them as such? Scheduling is no longer an issue. Collect and frame tattoo art from some of your favorite tattoo artists around the world by buying a skin and making an appointment and sending it to them. Once you get it back, frame it and hang it!

4x6 1/4 inch thick Not a practice pad! Like real skin! Collect Art! Frame it and Hang it!

Buy as a pack and save!
